{"tid":2413923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<大英> 英國2月消費者信心 創疫情以來最高 憧憬振興經濟","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T08:38:36.000Z","uid":227801,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef13b2e4f8a5acc5945452f101ac6941dfa2db2","tid":2413923,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576357-20210219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576357-20210219.htm&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69EB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=27df4561\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576357-20210219.htm&h=0153b503\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576357-20210219.htm</a><br />\n市場研究機構Gfk公布，2月英國消費者信心創近1年前疫情爆發以來最高，受惠於對疫苗接種計劃振興經濟的憧憬。<br />\n<br />\n2月英國消費者信心指數上升5點至負23，主要由於未來12個月經濟前景看法上升14點。市場原先預期指數微升至負27。<br />\n<br />\n用作衡量消費者購買大件商品意願的指數升至負19，但仍遠低於去年2月的正6。"},{"pid":"c83fbda43a6f8ffc465a4d71f7282e653c69d91a","tid":2413923,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"飯太 葉劉 陳智思 施永青 湯文說 ：fake news!"},{"pid":"45f96c07c3ea60680daa762f800b9d9baa342312","tid":2413923,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc9354d8f72eaaea27d6862bd51df29da51dd72","tid":2413923,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"千升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebae6b23b447239ef2be1e8ea856b54cc77bfc02","tid":2413923,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b6768c5eaa4619049ec42a4a02aa075b56cbc8","tid":241